<p>Wilder, Craig Steven, <em>Ebony and Ivy. Race, Slavery &amp; Troubled History of America’s Universities</em>. New York: Bloomsbury Press, 2013.</p>";i:2;s:0:"";i:3;s:28:"&w=100%&h=300px&edt=TinyMCE4";i:4;s:8:"richtext";}s:25:"issueArticleFootnotesText";a:5:{i:0;s:25:"issueArticleFootnotesText";i:1;s:17341:"<p><a href="#sdfootnote1anc" name="sdfootnote1sym">1</a> W.E.B. Du Bois, “The Perfect Vacation,” <em>The Crisis</em> 40, no. 8 (1931): 279.</p>
