<p><a href="#sdfootnote25anc" name="sdfootnote25sym">25</a> Jacques Rancière, <em>The Politics of Aesthetics</em>, trans. Gabriel Rockhill (London, New York: Bloomsbury, 2013).</p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote26anc" name="sdfootnote26sym">26</a> Noel W. Anderson, Andrew Weiner, “Questionnaire on Monuments,” <em>October</em> 165 (2018): 10.</p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote27anc" name="sdfootnote27sym">27</a> W.J.T. Mitchell, <em>What Do Pictures Want? The Lives and Loves of Images</em> (Chicago: University of Chicago Press, 2013), 132.</p>
